2026-04-06 Bootstrap project plan, product spec, README, and AGENTS guidance for the initial TermiWeb implementation.
2026-04-06 Scaffolded the first working TermiWeb app with shared workspace tabs, cookie auth, mobile terminal controls, local tests, and a production build path.
2026-04-06 Hardened shell resolution to prefer the default PowerShell 7 install path before PATH-based fallback behavior.
2026-04-06 Updated shell resolution precedence so PowerShell 7 from PATH wins, with the default install path used as a fallback before Windows PowerShell.
2026-04-06 Changed the default TermiWeb web port from 4317 to 22443 to avoid common telemetry-port collisions and match the preferred app identity.
2026-04-06 Added repo-root .env loading and fixed LAN host resolution so TERMIWEB_ALLOW_LAN=true works with the sample config.
2026-04-06 Refined the browser UI with clearer host identity, instance terminology, a collapsible instance rail, and a keyboard-style arrow cluster for mobile controls.
2026-04-06 Added shared-active-instance metadata, a select mode for copying terminal text, home-directory shell starts, and icon-based refresh/collapse controls.
2026-04-06 Made LAN binding the default path, added a fixed 120-column terminal width, swapped the rail icons, and exposed a Del key for mobile control.
2026-04-06 Stopped cross-device instance auto-following, made sidebar collapse local to each browser, switched select mode to a rendered viewport snapshot, narrowed the collapsed rail and control cluster, and changed the shared terminal width default to 40 columns.
2026-04-06 Removed the separate mobile layout in favor of one shared cross-device layout, doubled the main control density per row, separated collapsed instance close buttons from card hit targets, and changed the shared terminal width default to 80 columns.
2026-04-06 Removed page-level forced workspace width so phones fit the UI to the viewport again, while keeping zoom enabled and leaving overflow localized to the terminal surface.
2026-04-06 Switched the default viewport metadata to a desktop-style layout width so phones behave more like "Desktop Site" mode without requiring a per-device browser toggle.
2026-04-06 Removed the forced `initial-scale=1.0` from the desktop-style mobile viewport so browsers can choose a more zoomed-out initial fit on their own.
2026-04-06 Added `Home` and `End` to the compact mobile key cluster and placed them above the left and right arrow keys.
2026-04-06 Reworked `Ctrl` and `Alt` so a single tap arms the next key, a double tap locks the modifier, and the buttons visibly distinguish armed and locked states.
2026-04-06 Merged the terminal header into the main header, moved the terminal workspace into a top-aligned 4:3-aware stage, kept the sidebar outside the scaled stage, and defaulted the sidebar to collapsed on narrow viewports when no local preference exists.
2026-04-06 Moved the keyboard control tray out of the scaled workspace stage so the terminal buttons stay finger-sized on phones.
2026-04-06 Changed terminal sizing so 80 columns fit the available width while rows stay elastic, and aligned the cursor-key cluster beside the main control rows.
2026-04-06 Expanded the control tray into three taller main-button rows and matched the non-arrow button height to the cursor-key buttons for better touch targets.
2026-04-06 Changed the 4:3 stage behavior to keep full width and trim height instead of scaling the entire workspace down on narrow viewports.
2026-04-06 Tied the workspace shell to the live visual viewport height so the control tray stays above the on-screen keyboard on phones.
2026-04-06 Moved the control tray inside the outer terminal shell and reordered the main keys to Esc/Bksp/Del, Tab/Select/Copy, and Ctrl/Alt/Paste with Enter under the cursor cluster.
2026-04-06 Reused the lowest available auto-generated instance number, normalized legacy Terminal-style instance names forward to Instance naming, and enlarged the instance rail targets.
2026-04-06 Stacked the collapsed rail actions vertically so the collapse toggle sits above refresh instead of beside it.
2026-04-06 Added a findings log for dogfood issues and updated the repo workflow/docs to batch polish work from recorded findings.
2026-04-06 Fixed the first findings batch by making on-screen navigation keys application-cursor aware, stabilizing touch control focus and viewport refits, switching to a single solid terminal cursor, and auto-seeding Instance 1 when a login reaches an empty workspace.
2026-04-06 Tightened the first findings batch by giving on-screen Home and End a fallback sequence path and by reapplying the fitted desktop-style mobile viewport scale after orientation changes.
2026-04-06 Replaced the restart-time websocket reconnect flap with server recovery polling so live pages wait for the server and refresh themselves once it is back.
2026-04-06 Moved the control tray off synthetic mobile click handling onto direct touch/pointer activation, and increased the control tray key height while keeping the cursor cluster square.
